Angry IP Scanner is a fast and friendly network scanner.

It scans IP addresses and ports and can gather additional
information about network hosts.

Requirements:
  - SWT (Eclipse Standard Widget Toolkit)
  - Java 17 or newer

Installed files:
  /opt/ipscan
  /usr/bin/ipscan
  
Please note that it only supports 64-bit systems (x86_64).
32-bit architectures are not supported by the upstream developer
for this version.

Homepage:
  https://angryip.org/
